===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[do]] [[two]] or [[more]] [[thing]]s [[simultaneously]]; to [[hold]] a [[concurrent]] [[post]] or [[role]]; to [[combine]]
#: {{zh-x|總理 兼 外交部長{zhǎng}|Prime Minister and '''concurrently''' Minister of Foreign Affairs}}
#: {{zh-x|教練 兼 隊員|player-coach; playing coach}}
#: {{zh-x|兼管|to '''concurrently''' be in charge of}}
#* {{zh-x|魚，我 所-欲 也；熊掌，亦 我 所-欲 也，二 者 不可 得 兼，舍{shě} 魚 而 取 熊掌 者 也。生，亦 我 所-欲 也；義，亦 我 所-欲 也，二 者 不可 得 兼，舍{shě} 生 而 取 義 者 也。|I like fish, and I also like bear's paws. If I cannot have the two '''together''', I will let the fish go, and take the bear's paws. So, I like life, and I also like justice. If I cannot keep the two '''together''', I will let life go, and choose justice.|ref=Mengzi-L}}
# [[concurrently]]; [[simultaneously]]; [[combining]]; [[both]]
#: {{zh-x|兼 有 兩 性 特徵 的|having both sexual characteristics; androgynous}}
# {{lb|zh|obs-std}} [[double]]
#: {{zh-x|兼程|to travel at '''double''' speed}}
#: {{zh-x|兼旬|twenty days}}
#* {{zh-x|子曰：「^求 也 退，故 進 之；^由 也 兼 人，故 退 之。」|{{w|Confucius|The Master}} said: "{{w|Ran Qiu|(Ran) Qiu}} holds himself back. It is for this reason that I tried to urge him on. {{w|Zhong You|(Zhong) You}} has the energy of '''two''' men. It is for this reason that I tried to hold him back."|ref=Lunyu}}
# to amalgamate, to merge
#* {{zh-x|約 從 離 衡，兼 ^韓、^魏、^燕{yān}、^楚、^齊、^趙、^宋、^衛、^中山 之 眾。|They formed the Vertical Alliance and spurned the Horizontal Alliance, '''amalgamating''' the multitudes of Hán, Wèi, Yān, Chǔ, Zhào, Sòng, Wèy, and Zhōngshān.|ref={{lw|zh|賈誼}} ({{w|Jia Yi}}),《{{lw|zh|s:過秦論|過秦論}}》("{{w|Ten Crimes of Qin|Discourse on Qin's Faults}}")}}
# to annex, to absorb
#* {{zh-x|武、獻 以下，兼 國 多 矣。|From {{w|Duke Wu of Jin|Wu}} and {{w|Duke Xian of Jin|Xian}} afterwards, many states have been '''annexed''' (by {{w|Jin (state)|Jin}}).|ref=Zuozhuan}}
#* {{zh-x|萬乘 之 主 有能 服 術 行法，以 為{wéi} 亡-徵 之 君 風雨 者，其 兼-天下 不-難 矣。|If the sovereign of ten thousand chariots can exercise tact and enforce law and thereby function as gale and rain to rulers having portents of ruin, his '''annexation''' of All-under-Heaven will not be difficult.|ref=Hanfeizi-L}}
#* {{zh-x|富者 兼-地 數 萬 畝，貧者 無 容足 之 居。|The rich '''enclose''' several myriad acres of lands; the poor have no spot to dwell and stand their feet.|ref='''794 CE'''', {{lw|zh|陸贄}} ({{w|Lu Zhi (Tang dynasty)|Lu Zhi}}), {{lw|zh|s:均節賦稅恤百姓六條|均節賦稅恤百姓六條}} (''Six Proposals to Reform Taxation and to Help Out the Common People'')}}
